WEBVTT

00:24.310 --> 00:26.230
What is this place?

00:26.230 --> 00:33.070
It seems this castle fell into disrepair during
the revolution, abandoned and forgotten

00:33.070 --> 00:34.990
because it's in a remote location.

00:34.990 --> 00:40.950
I don't like when
those demons act like a lord.

00:41.740 --> 00:46.750
Are you sure that the villagers
were taken there?

00:46.750 --> 00:47.750
Yes.

00:47.750 --> 00:53.420
We even tracked them into the keep
last night, but we found nothing.

00:53.420 --> 00:56.550
They can't just disappear, you idiot.

00:56.550 --> 00:58.430
You're so easily fooled.

00:58.430 --> 01:00.090
My apologies.

01:00.090 --> 01:04.970
And today,
another woman disappeared.

01:04.970 --> 01:09.020
While we were on the lookout,
they took them right under our noses.

01:09.020 --> 01:12.360
I don't expect anything from you guys.

01:13.320 --> 01:17.900
Apparently, we're not too late.

01:17.900 --> 01:19.280
That bastard!

01:37.910 --> 01:41.630
I should have killed them last night.

02:39.730 --> 02:41.070
Got you!

02:47.780 --> 02:50.000
You guys, get back.

02:50.000 --> 02:53.000
The Wind Hashira and I
will take it from here.

02:53.000 --> 02:54.080
But...

02:54.080 --> 02:56.340
You guys are in our way.

02:56.340 --> 02:58.000
Just get the hell out of here.

03:01.340 --> 03:05.470
Shinazugawa,
something strange's going on here.

03:05.470 --> 03:08.560
Yeah, I don't like it.

03:08.560 --> 03:12.600
I've never seen so many demons
swarming in one place.

03:12.600 --> 03:14.190
Help me!

03:19.570 --> 03:22.820
Wind Breathing, Second Form:

03:28.200 --> 03:30.540
Claws-Purifying Wind!

03:35.920 --> 03:39.040
Serpent Breathing, Fifth Form:

03:47.220 --> 03:49.680
Slithering Serpent.

03:50.260 --> 03:51.640
That was close.

03:51.640 --> 03:53.520
I didn't ask for your help!

03:55.350 --> 03:59.480
This strength...
They're not ordinary demon hunters.

03:59.480 --> 04:00.440
They're Hashiras!

04:00.440 --> 04:02.190
Help me!

04:02.190 --> 04:03.360
Hey, demon!

04:03.360 --> 04:06.450
Leave that woman and your head here!

04:09.870 --> 04:12.580
They just keep appearing
one after another.

04:12.580 --> 04:14.960
Are you demons or cockroaches?

04:29.470 --> 04:31.350
There are still more?

04:34.430 --> 04:37.640
Where the hell are those demons
coming from?

04:37.640 --> 04:41.020
Save the woman, Shinazugawa.

04:41.020 --> 04:43.150
I got your six.

04:44.990 --> 04:47.360
Well, I'm getting bored, too.

04:47.360 --> 04:49.450
I let you take care of them.

04:52.870 --> 04:55.910
Serpent Breathing, Third Form:

05:02.590 --> 05:04.250
Coil Choke.

05:12.050 --> 05:15.930
Listen, you can't win even if
you gather small fries.

05:15.930 --> 05:18.640
Just give up and die.

05:30.560 --> 05:32.700
Wind Breathing,

05:32.700 --> 05:34.200
Fourth Form:

05:37.370 --> 05:40.040
Rising Dust Storm.

05:41.460 --> 05:43.000
Good grief.

05:43.000 --> 05:45.550
If you want her so badly...

05:45.550 --> 05:47.420
No! What are you going to do?

05:47.420 --> 05:48.670
Catch her!

06:04.690 --> 06:06.530
What?

06:26.750 --> 06:29.210
Stay there, shithead!

06:42.440 --> 06:44.480
What the heck is going on?

06:45.110 --> 06:49.360
Hey, Shinazugawa. What was that?

06:49.860 --> 06:52.610
Where have the demons gone?

06:54.450 --> 06:56.370
How the hell do I know?

07:14.680 --> 07:17.890
You sure you want to get off
at the end of this road?

07:47.710 --> 07:49.000
Miss Kanao!

07:49.000 --> 07:51.670
Good work on completing your mission!

07:51.670 --> 07:53.550
Good work!

08:11.860 --> 08:14.860
Master, I have just returned.

08:16.660 --> 08:21.660
That matter of the Swordsmith Village
was just like I told you the other day.

08:21.660 --> 08:31.450
Tokito, Kanroji, Kamado, and the others
have defeated two Upper Ranks.

08:31.450 --> 08:36.330
Moreover, Nezuko has overcome the sun.

08:36.330 --> 08:41.220
Hence, there will be
major developments to come.

08:41.640 --> 08:42.600
Yes.

08:43.220 --> 08:49.560
Probably, Muzan Kibutsuji will use
his demons to take Nezuko away.

08:51.020 --> 08:55.490
In order to own a demon that
overcomes the sun.

09:01.120 --> 09:08.210
I will attend an urgent Hashira meeting
at the Ubuyashiki residence.

09:08.920 --> 09:14.380
In the meantime,
can I ask you to protect Nezuko?

09:18.260 --> 09:20.220
It's a request.

09:22.260 --> 09:29.140
(Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba
Hashira Training Arc)

09:32.610 --> 09:36.150
I see. They're moving their base.

09:36.150 --> 09:38.650
Are the villagers all right?

09:38.990 --> 09:41.070
I don't know that much
about the details.

09:41.070 --> 09:43.780
The demons might attack at night,

09:43.780 --> 09:46.750
so they're desperately
rebuilding and relocating.

09:46.750 --> 09:48.160
Is that so?

09:48.160 --> 09:52.380
It's miraculous how that was all it took
even though two Upper Ranks attacked.

09:53.880 --> 09:56.840
The enemies were really strong.

10:03.390 --> 10:07.930
The Corps created several "empty villages"
for such occasions.

10:07.930 --> 10:10.440
So we're able to move quickly
if something happens.

10:10.440 --> 10:12.150
I see.

10:12.150 --> 10:16.480
Well, that's because the Master and
his family's predictions are incredible.

10:16.480 --> 10:19.530
Anyway, you've been unconscious
for a week.

10:19.530 --> 10:21.240
Is it okay to eat that much?

10:21.240 --> 10:25.070
Yes! Kanroji said she also eats a lot.

10:25.700 --> 10:29.120
Nah, she seems a bit beyond reason.

10:30.580 --> 10:32.250
Delicious!

10:32.580 --> 10:33.960
Is it true that Love and Mist

10:33.960 --> 10:37.210
slept for two days and were almost
fully recovered by the third day?

10:37.210 --> 10:39.130
It's true! I respect them!

10:39.130 --> 10:41.510
You're getting closer to them, you know?

10:41.510 --> 10:42.880
A bit by bit.

10:43.550 --> 10:46.930
Well, it's fine if you get better soon.

10:46.930 --> 10:48.140
Yes?

10:48.140 --> 10:50.140
I'm glad everyone is alive.

10:50.140 --> 10:51.140
Yes!

10:51.140 --> 10:54.020
Oh, this is what I wanted to ask the most.

10:54.020 --> 10:56.560
I heard your sister has become
something incredible.

10:56.560 --> 10:58.150
Is she all right?

10:58.150 --> 10:59.900
Yes, she is.

11:00.360 --> 11:04.070
She's starting to toddle under the sun.

11:05.870 --> 11:07.160
Isn't that bad?

11:07.160 --> 11:09.620
Seriously, isn't that dangerous?

11:09.620 --> 11:13.870
She's being examined,
but we still don't know anything.

11:13.870 --> 11:18.340
We don't know if she returning back
into a human or evolving as a demon.

11:18.960 --> 11:21.340
Is Lady Kocho looking into it?

11:21.340 --> 11:23.050
Not her, but Lady Tamayo.

11:23.050 --> 11:24.880
Who's Lady Tamayo?

11:27.140 --> 11:29.810
Hey, see? You ate too much!

11:29.810 --> 11:32.270
You should know that
you're still recovering.

11:33.060 --> 11:34.980
That was close.

11:36.190 --> 11:40.780
Your sister has become like that
and things are going to start happening.

11:40.780 --> 11:43.950
Every Corps member has been given
an order to be on alert.

11:43.950 --> 11:47.200
And we're told
the Hashiras are gathering.

11:47.200 --> 11:49.990
What happens from now on, really?

12:06.010 --> 12:08.260
We're the last ones, huh?

12:08.260 --> 12:11.680
Sorry for keeping you waiting.

12:12.140 --> 12:12.390
(Gyomei Himejima, the Stone Hashira)

12:12.390 --> 12:16.810
No problem.
Well done on your mission.
(Gyomei Himejima, the Stone Hashira)

12:16.810 --> 12:16.850
(Gyomei Himejima, the Stone Hashira)

12:17.150 --> 12:18.560
It's nothing.

12:19.940 --> 12:19.980
I heard Kanroji and Tokito
had a fight against the Upper Ranks.

12:19.980 --> 12:24.690
