12:31.200 --> 12:33.040
Right, Muichiro?

12:33.240 --> 12:33.870
(Muichiro Tokito, the Mist Hashira)

12:33.870 --> 12:35.000
Yeah.
(Muichiro Tokito, the Mist Hashira)

12:35.000 --> 12:36.580
(Muichiro Tokito, the Mist Hashira)

12:37.790 --> 12:39.880
That makes me jealous.

12:39.880 --> 12:43.920
Why haven't I ever encountered
any Upper Rank?

12:44.340 --> 12:44.380
It's like, almost everyone
is running into them.

12:44.380 --> 12:48.970
(Obanai Iguro, the Serpent Hashira)
It's like, almost everyone
